  "Description": {
    "English": "A pattern, no more than a mere waveform, etched into an ethereal shard of glass. This fragment of data represents a trace of the electrical impulses running across a neural network. Many fragments would be required to recreate any sensible experience.<br><br>Released upon the destruction of a <span class=\"name name-special\">boundary horror</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个仅仅是波形的图案，蚀刻在一片虚无缥缈的玻璃碎片的表面。这种数据碎片能呈现神经网络中电脉冲的痕迹。需要很多碎片才能重现有意义的体验。<br><br>摧毁<span class=\"name name-special\">边界惧物</span>时释放的产物。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個類似波形的圖案刻在縹緲的玻璃碎片上。這個資料碎片代表電子脈衝在神經網路傳遞的軌跡。需要收集許多碎片才能重新體驗其中的含意。<br><br>殲滅<span class=\"name name-special\">邊界懼獸</span>後產生。"
  },
